180.269, 181.3796, 180.8445, 181.7727, 180.3308, 180.2859, 180.7807, 179.8688, 181.0248, 179.8071, 179.7855, 180.0896, 181.9567, 181.3182, 180.9301, 182.2591, 184.1495, 185.5339, 190.4586, 193.0695, 191.6363, 191.5352, 190.0328, 192.2137, 191.037, 191.7294, 191.1988, 190.282, 189.0082, 188.8936, 188.8721, 187.7895, 188.4468, 187.7304, 188.1189, 189.7157, 189.7883, 189.3248, 189.2939, 187.8911, 187.652, 188.0783, 190.3588, 190.5119, 190.6268, 191.6696, 190.3971, 191.0483, 191.4021, 192.5959, 192.8215, 192.3883, 191.9914, 192.1088, 193.0278, 193.8028, 194.4392, 193.432, 196.3822, 196.426, 199.9076, 199.3921, 200.2756, 202.5468, 203.311, 205.121, 203.0092, 200.1078, 200.8486, 198.6824, 199.8019, 201.6585, 200.5106, 200.3156, 200.3622, 200.3971, 201.0474, 199.7662, 199.0249, 200.159, 199.5289, 197.2114, 197.3362, 197.3829, 199.5846, 201.5215, 203.0489, 202.9472, 202.1632, 202.3896, 204.7321, 204.7376, 203.511, 202.9913, 205.4349, 206.9116, 207.3419, 209.8871, 205.9983, 203.1855, 203.1042, 202.4959, 203.6719, 204.7993, 203.9342, 204.0183, 204.9766, 205.8481, 205.2166, 203.374, 203.7256, 204.6939, 205.156, 205.4922, 205.3709, 205.0245, 204.5498, 201.0608, 203.6814, 204.2373, 203.826, 203.4349, 205.1151, 204.5308, 205.0039, 203.7875, 204.5961, 204.0248, 201.925, 200.9254, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>Weekly Momentum in Commodity Futures -- Factor Summary</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>论文发现商品期货中存在显著的短期动量效应（weekly momentum），与股票市场的短期反转截然不同。论文将过去52周分解为4个不重叠子区间，发现1周动量（CMOM_{1,1}）是最强且最稳健的因子，无法被carry、股票动量或套保压力解释。</p>\n<p>在中国商品期货上复现时，<strong>年度动量</strong>（CMOM_{52,27}，即跳过近6个月、使用前6个月的回报率）表现最优，Sharpe达1.19。这可能反映了中国商品期货市场的微观结构差异——更长周期的动量信号在A股商品期货上更有效。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.05</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-11.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.07</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3190</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.4</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.14 / 1.16</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.97</td><td>1.28</td><td>0.8</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.73</span></td><td>1.01</td><td>0.2</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.7</span></td><td>0.55</td><td>0.4</td><td>1.11</td><td>0.27</td><td>1.91</td><td>0.17</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3192</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>40.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>15.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>论文定义四种动量信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{CMOM}_{k_1, k_2} = \\text{sort commodities by} \\sum_{t=t_0-k_1}^{t_0-k_2} r_{i,t}</div>\n<p>具体为：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{1,1}</span>: 过去1周收益（日频约5天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{4,2}</span>: 过去第2-4周收益（日频约6-20天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{26,5}</span>: 过去第5-26周收益（日频约21-130天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{52,27}</span>: 过去第27-52周收益（日频约131-260天）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>最优实现使用 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{52,27}</span>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i = \\frac{P_{i,t-130}}{P_{i,t-260}} - 1</div>\n<p>截面排名后取top 20% long、bottom 20% short，IC-gate过滤弱品种，vol-target缩放。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>R1</strong>: 实现论文4种动量子区间 + combo。结果：yearly_mom_252d_raw Sharpe 1.19 最强，weekly_mom_5d_raw Sharpe -0.15 最弱。与论文发现的\"weekly最强\"相反，中国商品市场上长期动量更有效。</li>\n<li><strong>R2</strong>: 扩展参数网格（lookback x hold_days），添加12-1经典动量。yr_mom_h10_raw Sharpe 1.08，未超过R1最优。</li>\n<li><strong>R3</strong>: 细化quintile阈值（15%/20%/30%）、连续信号、IC-gating。yr_q20_h5_ic_raw 达到Sharpe 1.19，与R1最优持平。决策=skip（通过）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（57个），黑色系（HC/JM/RB）和油脂（P）贡献最大</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每5天换仓，信号lookback 260天</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 年度Sharpe波动较大（2019/2021/2024偏低），说明长期动量在趋势不明确年份表现偏弱</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.33s</li>\n</ul>"}